trans-unit.source: Provides common methods and properties for composite activity designers that contain structured layouts.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder vanlige metoder og egenskaper for sammensatte aktiviteter utviklere som inneholder strukturert oppsett.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner is the base class for all designers that contain child designers and the child designers are connected to each other using lines rendered on the design surface, called connectors.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner er basisklasse for alle utviklere som inneholder underordnede utviklere og underordnede utviklere er koblet til ved hjelp av linjer gjengis på utformingsoverflaten kall koblinger.

trans-unit.source: The class is provided so that activity designer developers can provide a number of activity designer layout types, rather than being tied to the layout provided in the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen er angitt slik at aktiviteten designer utviklere kan angi flere typer for aktivitet designer oppsett, i stedet for som er knyttet til oppsettet i <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner>klasse.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Draws all of the connectors to display on the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Tegner alle koblingene til å vise på den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Connectors are links between separate designers on a workflow design surface.
trans-unit.target: Koblinger er koblinger mellom separate utviklere på en arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: These links appear as lines on the design surface and each line end connects to a visible point on the designers it connects.
trans-unit.target: Disse koblingene vises som linjer på utformingsoverflaten og hver linjeende som kobler til et synlige punkt på utviklere den kobles.

trans-unit.source: These points are called connection points.
trans-unit.target: Disse punkt kalles tilkoblingen punkt.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Drawing.Size"> </xref> som representerer den nye størrelsen på den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> på arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: Displays the designer verbs associated with a smart tag at a specified location on the workflow design surface.
trans-unit.target: Viser designer verb som er tilknyttet en smart kode på en angitt plassering på arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Drawing.Point"></xref> that represents the location on the workflow design surface for which to show <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerAction"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Drawing.Point"> </xref> som representerer plassering på arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten å vise <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerAction"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Notifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref> when the current designer view changes.
trans-unit.target: Varsler den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> når gjeldende designer vise endringene.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView"></xref> that is to be set.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView"> </xref> som er angis.

trans-unit.source: Stores the current view state of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref> to a binary stream.
trans-unit.target: Lagrer gjeldende visningsstatusen for den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> til en binær dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IO.BinaryWriter> to which the current designer view state is stored.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IO.BinaryWriter>gjeldende designer visningsstatusen er lagret.</xref:System.IO.BinaryWriter>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref> displays smart tags.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> viser smart koder.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the designer displays smart tags; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis designer viser smart koder. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a read-only collection of designer actions that are associated with the smart tags on the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter en skrivebeskyttet samling designer handlinger som er knyttet til smartkortet koder i utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The collection is returned only if the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner> hosts multiple views.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen returneres bare hvis det <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner>vert flere visninger.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner.Views%2A> property to determine how many views the current designer hosts.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner.Views%2A>til å fastslå hvor mange viser gjeldende designer verter.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner.Views%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerAction"></xref> read-only collection that contains all the actions associated with the smart tags on the designer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerAction"> </xref> skrivebeskyttet samling som inneholder alle handlinger som er knyttet til smartkortet koder i utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Get a read-only collection of designer views that the current <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref> hosts.
trans-unit.target: Få en skrivebeskyttet samling designer visninger som gjeldende <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> vert.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView"></xref> read-only collection that contains the views hosted by the current <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView"> </xref> skrivebeskyttet samling som inneholder visninger ved gjeldende <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.StructuredCompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref>.
